* Snow Tech sighs and looks at Iron Raptor closely. She looked tired and fed 
up, but that was his evaluation, she could be happy for all he knew. He 
hadn't seen her in years, and she had obviously overgone some....changes. 
His eye's welled up atthe thought of the good-ol-days, when they where 
little and played together in the palace gardens while their parents 
visited. A large tear feel from his eye, he missed those good-ol days. He 
wailed and wraped his arms around her laegs, crying.*

" I MISSED YOU!!! WAAAAAAAIIIIIIILLLLL!!!!!"

* Shadow Cat stepped back in suprise and looked at him. Had he lost his 
diodes or something? She looked at Iron Raptor and sighed*

" Just kick him in the head, i'm sure it'll jam back into place, whatever it 
is..."
